WEBVTT

00:00.403 --> 00:01.971
<i>Previously on Fringe...</i>

00:02.037 --> 00:03.072
How does she seem?

00:03.123 --> 00:04.123
Like Olivia Dunham.

00:04.207 --> 00:05.658
She's internalized her traits.

00:05.742 --> 00:08.577
For all intents and purposes,
she is our agent Dunham.

00:08.628 --> 00:10.729
You're imbedding
one of them on my team?

00:10.797 --> 00:12.081
What if her new identity
doesn't hold?

00:12.148 --> 00:14.717
Then she'll no longer
be necessary.

00:14.784 --> 00:17.036
So you know things
about the other side.

00:17.103 --> 00:18.888
Things you couldn't know
unless you were from there.

00:18.955 --> 00:19.922
Like what?

00:19.990 --> 00:21.624
Your niece is alive.

00:21.691 --> 00:23.542
She was born, and it's
her birthday today.

00:23.610 --> 00:24.927
There's no way to prove it.

00:24.978 --> 00:26.512
Yes, there is.

00:26.596 --> 00:29.298
Their Olivia can
travel between worlds safely.

00:29.349 --> 00:31.684
We believe you may be
able to the same.

00:36.990 --> 00:38.240
Aunt Liv!

00:38.308 --> 00:40.542
I knew you wouldn't
forget my birthday.

00:40.610 --> 00:42.411
Ahh! It didn't work.

00:42.478 --> 00:44.597
All I saw was black.

